<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Types_of_pollution">Types of pollution</span></h2>
<ul class="gallery mw-gallery-packed" style="">
	<li class="gallerycaption">Types of pollution (click to enlarge)</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 198.697px;"><div style="width: 198.697px;">
		
<p>Point source water pollution.<sup id="cite_ref-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-3">[3]</a></sup>
</p>
			</div>
		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 192.375px;"><div style="width: 192.375px;">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 190.734px;"><div style="margin:0px auto;"><a href="javascript: void(0)" class="image"><img alt="" src="https://energyeducation.ca/wiki/images/thumb/3/3b/Pswaterpol.jpg/280px-Pswaterpol.jpg" decoding="async" width="190" height="147" srcset="/wiki/images/thumb/0/04/Smokestackse.jpg/407px-Smokestackse.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/images/thumb/0/04/Smokestackse.jpg/543px-Smokestackse.jpg 2x"></a></div></div>
			<div class="gallerytext">
<p>Point source air pollution.<sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-4">[4]</a></sup>
