		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 198.697px;"><div style="width: 198.697px;">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 197.056px;"><div style="margin:0px auto;"><a href="javascript: void(0)" class="image"><img alt="" src="https://energyeducation.ca/wiki/images/thumb/0/04/Smokestackse.jpg/271px-Smokestackse.jpg" decoding="async" width="197" height="147" srcset="/wiki/images/thumb/0/08/Soilcontam.jpg/420px-Soilcontam.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/images/thumb/0/08/Soilcontam.jpg/560px-Soilcontam.jpg 2x"></a></div></div>
