		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 204.637px;"><div style="width: 204.637px;">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 202.325px;"><div style="margin:0px auto;"><a href="javascript: void(0)" class="image"><img alt="" src="https://energyeducation.ca/wiki/images/thumb/0/08/Soilcontam.jpg/280px-Soilcontam.jpg" decoding="async" width="202" height="147" srcset="/wiki/images/thumb/e/e1/Lightpol.jpg/430px-Lightpol.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/images/thumb/e/e1/Lightpol.jpg/573px-Lightpol.jpg 2x"></a></div></div>
			<div class="gallerytext">
